    <main>
      <h2>Chance Encounter (Ichigo Ichie)</h2>
      
      <div class="content">
	<p>
	  Speaking to you again<br>
	  The joy comes flooding back<br>
	  Hearing your dulcet voice<br>
	  Fills the heart;
	</p>

	<p>
	  The sound of your laugh<br>
	  Cracks the heavens<br>
	  Like a brilliant comet;<br>
	  The rareness of your appearance
	</p>

	<p>
	  Only makes your light more dazzling<br>
	  As it runs across the night sky;<br>
	  All the stars take a bow to you<br>
	  May you never lose your way.
	</p>
      </div>
      
